{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":325922,"duration_api_ms":224718,"num_turns":36,"result":"Done. Here's the summary:\n\n## Fix PM-S87-03 — Disabled CTA button styling\n\n**Problem:** The \"Send to waiter\" button in the cart drawer was always green (`bg-green-600`) even when disabled (`isTableVerified === false`), misleading users into thinking they could tap it.\n\n**Fix in `CartView.jsx` (lines 1204-1220):**\n- **Conditional className:** When `isTableVerified === false` → `bg-gray-300 text-gray-500 cursor-not-allowed hover:bg-gray-300` (gray, faded). Otherwise → `bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700` (green, active).\n- **Hint text:** Added `tr('cart.enter_table_code_hint', 'Введите код стола чтобы отправить заказ')` below the button when disabled.\n- When `isSubmitting` (order in progress), the button stays green with \"Отправка...\" text — only the table-not-verified state gets gray styling.\n\n**Commits:** `b2449d0` (pre-review + fix), `ab5c17b` (docs). Pushed to remote.","stop_reason":null,"session_id":"82047d27-dd34-4253-a827-0701373887ee","total_cost_usd":1.1321335,"usage":{"input_tokens":844,"cache_creation_input_tokens":62888,"cache_read_input_tokens":1014859,"output_tokens":8293,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":62888,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":844,"outputTokens":8293,"cacheReadInputTokens":1014859,"cacheCreationInputTokens":62888,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":1.1120244999999997,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000},"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001":{"inputTokens":5339,"outputTokens":686,"cacheReadInputTokens":0,"cacheCreationInputTokens":9072,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.020109000000000005,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"uuid":"7f9005ec-e928-4ce0-8ae6-fc91d97e36d5"}
